snippet: Two late goals allowed the Serbians to win, 2-0, and avenge a bitter match last year that was ended when a drone flew over the field.
abstract: Soccer Roundup; Serbia defeats Albania, 2-0, in 2016 European Championship qualifier; other scores and news noted.
lead_paragraph: Two late goals allowed the Serbians to win, 2-0, and avenge a bitter match last year that was ended when a drone flew over the field.

headline.main: Serbia Wins in Albania Amid Heavy Security
headline.print_headline: Tense Euro Qualifying Match in Albania Ends With a Quiet Serbian Victory
